WEBVTT

00:06:29.760 --> 00:06:32.896
As he asked for this, God
changed his demeanor and said,

00:06:32.920 --> 00:06:34.760
“He is intoxicated. Put him aside."

00:06:35.670 --> 00:06:38.880
(Applause)

00:06:38.880 --> 00:06:42.656
"When he is sober, he can
ask for some other wish."

00:06:42.680 --> 00:06:45.576
Now don’t think
that the priestess was harsh.

00:06:45.600 --> 00:06:48.656
No, please don’t think that.

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:52.810
Just imagine how difficult it must
be for her to put up with a man

00:06:52.810 --> 00:06:56.376
who is so self-obsessed that he wants
everyone to be charmed by his persona.

00:06:56.390 --> 00:07:01.256
Men have this tendency, as they go
up the ladder of success in life,